{"tid":1382360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生石灰加水放熱 沖涼唔好停水 會燒傷","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:53:01.000Z","uid":69967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"500ba7fe3c53c8a5c83772735299aee69958aff9","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"貴陽市一名男子魏先生在洗澡期間發現無水，到樓下向保安反映時，保安承認「水是我們停的」。而魏先生在詢問期間突感全身疼痛，求醫後證實因長時間沒沖走身上的肥皂引致鹼燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都是肥皂惹的禍？<br />\n<br />\n其實肥皂裡面必定會有鹼性物質，需要使用氫氧化鈉等強鹼來製作肥皂，不過一般肥皂的強鹼成分會在皂化過程與油脂反應後，變成脂肪酸鈉和甘油，呈現弱鹼性。<br />\n<br />\n是次事件應與男子使用的肥皂品質不佳，或因過長時間未沖走身上的肥皂所致。事主魏先生更需留醫，其後向保安及物業管理投訴不果，保安拒絕承擔有關住院費用，物業管理辦事處更是大門緊鎖，電話亦無人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強鹼燒傷應如何處理？<br />\n<br />\n常見的強鹼有氫氧化鈉（苛性鈉）及石灰等，強鹼對人體的皮膚組織的損害力比強酸更重，因為強鹼可滲透深入組織，使組織蛋白髮生溶解。<br />\n<br />\n急救方法：若不慎接觸到有關物質，應立即用清水反覆沖洗至少20分鐘（生石灰除外），亦可用食醋來清洗，中和皮膚的鹼液。生石灰燒傷則應用毛巾抹淨皮膚上的生石灰顆粒，才用水沖洗患處，因生石灰遇水時會發生化學反應，產生大量熱力灼傷皮膚，需要小心處理。"},{"pid":"f389469982d798b82d632a0bec496b406e35c85c","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"記得唔好吸入生石灰 口腔同肺部有水 會引致燒傷"},{"pid":"5e89c7e801c636abdb00bdb62122cfaca1cfb51a","tid":1382360,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我無野講 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"299c9acf32100495f2f00449533967fa624cb537","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"生石灰唔係路由器 唔係針 無法燃燒同攻擊"},{"pid":"ceb22c9305aaa32a556c0d875f76402a8ad4c7e9","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f856372c9b2b0f4996d4b39d8e43a13bbbc8244f","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1351f91d9da29a1e48f2caa4e4c9be3c9f1f175","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"476aa6121ebb8e96969ad7083bb8f11ea4991ec4","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"讓大家了解生石灰禍害"},{"pid":"86083b268807ebb2f5f492b8427df8f6538ab63c","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a07f2e2f05bf0b85160987f14dfbefd76a2aaf0","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97add19d0a854fb33623e1e88c7036e93dce170e","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1653abe5da397ad14b91e29f7114b3dee539b1d6","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac192d7d5606a5893c0e349dd1a0bbb5f3643e74","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"十連了"},{"pid":"cda2b59d75f0571d5d0339e71a8ed22213d05639","tid":1382360,"uid":69967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"十"}]}